      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 3,
      "text": "統計之機器學習基礎應用",
      "pageIndex": 8,
      "bbox": [
        168.87,
        154.3,
        368.01,
        171.96
      ],
      "id": "block-2",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "depth": 3,
      "title": "1. 前言與章節導覽",
      "anchor": "1前言與章節導覽",
      "pageIndex": 8,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        203.11,
        203.57,
        218.12
      ],
      "id": "block-3",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 4,
      "text": "在真實世界中，資料往往受限於觀察條件、取樣變異或內在隨機性，使得預測結果不具唯一性與確定性。因此，機器學習模型的核心任務，並非僅在於尋找絕對規則，而是要能處理資料中不可避免的「不確定性」，並在此基礎上進行合理的預測與決策。這正是機率與統計在機器學習中扮演關鍵角色的原因。",
      "pageIndex": 8,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        230.3,
        517.96,
        317.54
      ],
      "id": "block-4",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 4,
      "text": "本節將介紹機率與統計在建構機器學習模型時的實務應用，說明如何運用隨機變數、機率分佈來表示資料行為，進而透過條件機率、貝氏定理等概念進行推論與模型更新。同時，也會探討統計推論（如假設檢定、p 值計算）在模型評估與特徵選擇等任務中的操作方法。",
      "pageIndex": 8,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        330.29,
        518.15,
        417.5
      ],
      "id": "block-5",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "depth": 3,
      "title": "2. 資料與隨機變數的機率表示",
      "anchor": "2資料與隨機變數的機率表示",
      "pageIndex": 8,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        453.12,
        274.0,
        468.13
      ],
      "id": "block-6",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 4,
      "text": "在建構機器學習模型時，其核心邏輯通常可表述為：「在特定觀察條件下，某結果發生的可能性有多大。」這意味著我們並非尋求唯一解，而是學習一種條件機率分佈（Conditional Probability Distribution）。",
      "pageIndex": 8,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        480.31,
        518.32,
        542.56
      ],
      "id": "block-7",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 4,
      "text": "其形式可表示為：P（Y｜X），其中X 為輸入特徵（Feature）、Y 為目標變數 （Label）。這樣的機率模型有兩種意涵：",
      "pageIndex": 8,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        554.23,
        518.4,
        592.6
      ],
      "id": "block-8",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "預測導向：模型輸出為某結果的機率（如分類機率），而非確定性分類結果。",
      "pageIndex": 8,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        604.11,
        521.88,
        617.56
      ],
      "id": "block-9",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "不確定性評估：機率反映了模型對預測的信心程度，有助於風險控制與決策制定。",
      "pageIndex": 8,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        629.1,
        517.91,
        667.63
      ],
      "id": "block-10",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 4,
      "text": "在以機率方式理解資料時，我們會根據資料型態的不同，區分為離散型與連續型隨機變數，並透過不同的機率分佈來加以建模。這些機率分佈不僅可用來表示資料的行為特性，也可作為機器學習模型假設的基礎架構，影響模型選擇與參數學習方式。根據隨機變數的特性，機率分佈可以分為離散型和連續型兩大類：",
      "pageIndex": 8,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        680.38,
        520.68,
        767.58
      ],
      "id": "block-11",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "depth": 4,
      "title": "（1）離散型機率分佈（Discrete Probability Distribution）",
      "anchor": "1離散型機率分佈discreteprobabilitydistribution",
      "pageIndex": 9,
      "bbox": [
        70.24,
        100.82,
        396.45,
        114.11
      ],
      "id": "block-12",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "離散型隨機變數：",
      "pageIndex": 9,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        125.62,
        223.03,
        139.07
      ],
      "id": "block-13",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "值是有限或可數的，例如擲骰子的結果（1、2、3、4、5、6）或某電商平台每日訂單數（0、1、2…）。這些變數的值通常為整數，且可能取值集合是明確的。",
      "pageIndex": 9,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        150.7,
        518.24,
        214.07
      ],
      "id": "block-14",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "離散型機率分佈：",
      "pageIndex": 9,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        225.7,
        223.03,
        239.15
      ],
      "id": "block-15",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "透過機率質量函數（Probability Mass Function, PMF）描述隨機變數「每一個特定取值的機率」。",
      "pageIndex": 9,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        250.69,
        518.29,
        289.1
      ],
      "id": "block-16",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "例如，擲骰子時，PMF 為P（X=1）=1/6，P（X=2）=1/6，",
      "pageIndex": 9,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        300.73,
        464.64,
        314.18
      ],
      "id": "block-17",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "PMF 總和等於1：",
      "pageIndex": 9,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        325.69,
        239.71,
        339.14
      ],
      "id": "block-18",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "= 1 ∑𝑃(𝑋= 𝑥𝑖) 𝑥𝑖",
      "pageIndex": 9,
      "bbox": [
        138.04,
        354.17,
        232.63,
        383.69
      ],
      "id": "block-19",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "常見分佈",
      "pageIndex": 9,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        399.61,
        172.6,
        413.06
      ],
      "id": "block-20",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "伯努利分佈（Bernoulli）：用於表示具有兩種可能結果的事件，例如成功與失敗、點擊與否等，常見於二元分類任務。",
      "pageIndex": 9,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        424.57,
        518.0,
        463.12
      ],
      "id": "block-21",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "二項分佈（Binomial）：描述在n 次獨立試驗中，某事件發生的次數，常用於模擬多次伯努利事件的累計行為。",
      "pageIndex": 9,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        474.63,
        518.17,
        513.04
      ],
      "id": "block-22",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "泊松分佈（Poisson）：描述在固定時間或空間區間中，某事件發生的次數。此分佈常應用於模擬稀有事件，例如單位時間內的客服來電數量、網頁伺服器的請求次數等。泊松分佈假設事件發生彼此獨立，且平均發生率為常數。",
      "pageIndex": 9,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        524.67,
        521.35,
        613.12
      ],
      "id": "block-23",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "depth": 4,
      "title": "（2）連續型機率分佈（Continuous Probability Distribution）",
      "anchor": "2連續型機率分佈continuousprobabilitydistribution",
      "pageIndex": 9,
      "bbox": [
        70.24,
        649.78,
        414.69,
        663.07
      ],
      "id": "block-24",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "連續型隨機變數：",
      "pageIndex": 9,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        674.7,
        223.03,
        688.15
      ],
      "id": "block-25",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "值是無限且連續的，通常用於描述測量型變數，如身高、體重、時間或溫度。這些變數不僅包含整數，還可以是任意實數，例如某病患等待時間可能為5.3 分鐘或5.31 分鐘。",
      "pageIndex": 9,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        699.66,
        518.32,
        763.14
      ],
      "id": "block-26",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "連續型機率分佈：",
      "pageIndex": 10,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        100.66,
        223.03,
        114.11
      ],
      "id": "block-27",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "透過機率密度函數（Probability Density Function, PDF）描述隨機變數 「於某取值範圍內的機率」。",
      "pageIndex": 10,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        125.62,
        518.25,
        164.15
      ],
      "id": "block-28",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "對於連續型隨機變數X，PDF 必須滿足以下條件：",
      "pageIndex": 10,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        175.66,
        416.73,
        189.11
      ],
      "id": "block-29",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "𝑏 𝑃(𝑎≤𝑋≤𝑏) = ∫𝑓(𝑥)𝑑𝑥 𝑎 其中，f（x）是隨機變數X 的機率密度函數（PDF），描述了隨機變數在區間[a, b]內的機率。",
      "pageIndex": 10,
      "bbox": [
        120.76,
        196.32,
        518.29,
        276.62
      ],
      "id": "block-30",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "常見的分佈",
      "pageIndex": 10,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        288.13,
        202.15,
        301.58
      ],
      "id": "block-31",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "常態分佈（Normal）：對稱的鐘型分佈，是最常見的連續型分佈，廣泛應用於誤差建模、參數估計、特徵分數標準化與生成模型。",
      "pageIndex": 10,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        313.09,
        517.99,
        351.62
      ],
      "id": "block-32",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "均勻分佈（Uniform）：表示在某個固定區間內，所有數值具有相同的發生機率，常用於初始化參數或隨機抽樣。",
      "pageIndex": 10,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        363.13,
        518.14,
        401.54
      ],
      "id": "block-33",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "指數分佈（Exponential）：指數分佈描述的是事件發生之間的間隔時間，適用於隨機過程中等待時間的分佈，通常用來描述「等待時間」 或「生存時間」。例如，機器故障時間、電話來電間隔等都可以用指數分佈來建模。該分佈的特徵是無記憶性（Memoryless），即未來的事件發生與過去的時間無關。",
      "pageIndex": 10,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        413.17,
        524.23,
        526.6
      ],
      "id": "block-34",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 7,
      "marker": "○",
      "text": "卡方分佈（Chi-square）：主要用於描述一組獨立標準常態分佈變數平方和的分佈結果，廣泛應用於統計檢定領域，特別是在變異數分析、卡方適合度檢定、列聯表獨立性檢定等情境中。",
      "pageIndex": 10,
      "bbox": [
        136.12,
        538.11,
        521.03,
        601.6
      ],
      "id": "block-35",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "在模型設計過程中，選用的機率分佈代表對資料生成機制的先驗假設。舉例來說，邏輯迴歸模型假設目標變數服從伯努利分佈，用以處理二元分類問題；線性迴歸則假設誤差項符合常態分佈，藉此推導參數估計與檢定的統計性質。至於生成模型（例如變分自編碼器，Variational Autoencoder），則更進一步將潛在變數與觀察變數的分佈型態納入模型架構核心，使機率分佈不只是輔助工具，而是模型運作本身的一部分。",
      "pageIndex": 10,
      "bbox": [
        120.76,
        622.54,
        521.76,
        759.78
      ],
      "id": "block-36",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "depth": 3,
      "title": "3. 條件機率與貝氏推論",
      "anchor": "3條件機率與貝氏推論",
      "pageIndex": 11,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        99.67,
        231.76,
        114.68
      ],
      "id": "block-37",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "depth": 4,
      "title": "（1）條件機率",
      "anchor": "1條件機率",
      "pageIndex": 11,
      "bbox": [
        70.24,
        125.78,
        155.2,
        139.07
      ],
      "id": "block-38",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "在機器學習中，除了觀察變數本身的分佈外，同時關注當已知某些條件（例如輸入特徵）時，如何推估另一個變數（如目標標籤）的可能性。這種在給定條件下估算機率的行為，即為條件機率（Conditional Probability）的概念。條件機率不僅是理解機器學習的邏輯核心，也構成了貝氏推論（Bayesian Inference）的基礎架構。",
      "pageIndex": 11,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        151.94,
        518.37,
        264.14
      ],
      "id": "block-39",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "條件機率的數學定義為：",
      "pageIndex": 11,
      "bbox": [
        101.8,
        275.81,
        243.43,
        289.1
      ],
      "id": "block-40",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "𝑃(𝐴|𝐵) = 𝑃(𝐴∩𝐵) 𝑃(𝐵)",
      "pageIndex": 11,
      "bbox": [
        101.8,
        301.16,
        205.03,
        330.81
      ],
      "id": "block-41",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "表示在事件B 發生的前提下，事件A 發生的機率。這種推論形式在分類、推薦、風險預測等領域皆有廣泛應用。以下舉例條件機率在機器學習中的應用場景：",
      "pageIndex": 11,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        341.57,
        521.88,
        379.94
      ],
      "id": "block-42",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "分類任務中的條件預測：模型的任務通常是學習條件機率P（Y｜X），即在觀察輸入特徵X 的情況下，預測Y 的可能性分佈。像是邏輯迴歸、貝氏分類器等，皆以此為核心。",
      "pageIndex": 11,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        391.45,
        518.38,
        454.96
      ],
      "id": "block-43",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "生醫與金融風控領域的風險預測：當已知某些檢驗結果或行為模式，條件機率可協助預估未來事件發生的可能性，例如罹病風險、違約機率等。",
      "pageIndex": 11,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        466.47,
        518.32,
        504.88
      ],
      "id": "block-44",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "生成模型中的變數關聯建構：在變分自編碼器或隱馬可夫模型（Hidden Markov Model, HMM）中，條件機率用於建構潛在變數與觀察變數間的依存關係。",
      "pageIndex": 11,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        516.51,
        521.8,
        579.88
      ],
      "id": "block-45",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "depth": 4,
      "title": "（2）貝氏定理",
      "anchor": "2貝氏定理",
      "pageIndex": 11,
      "bbox": [
        70.24,
        616.66,
        155.2,
        629.95
      ],
      "id": "block-46",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "機器學習模型的常見目標之一、是推估條件機率P（Y｜X），也就是在已知某些輸入條件X 的情況下，預測Y 的可能性。這種條件推論不僅存在於分類與推薦系統，也廣泛應用於風險預測、醫療診斷與生成模型等場景。隨著模型運作過程中不斷有新資料進入，若能根據這些資料即時調整對事件的預期，就能提升預測品質與模型靈活度。",
      "pageIndex": 11,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        641.62,
        518.4,
        771.54
      ],
      "id": "block-47",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "貝氏定理（Bayes' Theorem）正是處理這類條件推論問題的核心工具。建立在條件機率之上，是一種利用已知條件更新事件發生機率的方法：",
      "pageIndex": 12,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        100.82,
        518.01,
        139.07
      ],
      "id": "block-48",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "𝑃(𝐴|𝐵) = 𝑃(𝐵|𝐴) ∙𝑃(𝐴) 𝑃(𝐵) 此公式表示：在事件B 已發生的情況下，重新評估事件A 發生機率的方式。",
      "pageIndex": 12,
      "bbox": [
        101.8,
        151.13,
        521.49,
        204.83
      ],
      "id": "block-49",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "其四個構成元素如下：",
      "pageIndex": 12,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        216.62,
        205.63,
        229.91
      ],
      "id": "block-50",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "P（A）：",
      "pageIndex": 12,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        241.42,
        169.6,
        254.87
      ],
      "id": "block-51",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "先驗機率（Prior Probability）— 在尚未觀察事件B 之前，對事件A 發生的「初始信念」或「預設機率」。",
      "pageIndex": 12,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        266.41,
        518.4,
        304.94
      ],
      "id": "block-52",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "P（B｜A）：",
      "pageIndex": 12,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        316.45,
        190.63,
        329.9
      ],
      "id": "block-53",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "條件機率，或稱似然（Likelihood）— 在事件A 發生的前提下，事件B 發生的可能性。",
      "pageIndex": 12,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        341.41,
        518.72,
        379.94
      ],
      "id": "block-54",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "P（B）：",
      "pageIndex": 12,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        391.45,
        169.0,
        404.9
      ],
      "id": "block-55",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "邊際機率（Marginal Probability）— 事件B 發生的總體機率，亦為所有可能A 條件下B 發生機率的加權總和。（無論A 是否發生，B 發生的整體可能性。）",
      "pageIndex": 12,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        416.41,
        518.4,
        479.92
      ],
      "id": "block-56",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "P（A｜B）：",
      "pageIndex": 12,
      "bbox": [
        102.16,
        491.43,
        190.63,
        504.88
      ],
      "id": "block-57",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "後驗機率（Posterior Probability）— 在觀察到事件B 之後，根據新的資訊更新後，對事件A 發生機率的重新估計。",
      "pageIndex": 12,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        516.51,
        518.28,
        554.92
      ],
      "id": "block-58",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 6,
      "marker": "◦",
      "text": "這是貝式定理的核心輸出。",
      "pageIndex": 12,
      "bbox": [
        120.52,
        566.43,
        290.35,
        579.88
      ],
      "id": "block-59",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "貝氏定理的關鍵意涵，在於可以將「原有知識」與「新資料觀察」整合起來，產生即時的後驗機率調整。這種更新能力，使得機器學習模型在面對不確定性與資料稀疏問題時，能保有推論的彈性與解釋力。",
      "pageIndex": 12,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        605.71,
        521.44,
        667.99
      ],
      "id": "block-60",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "depth": 3,
      "title": "4. 假設檢定與統計推論",
      "anchor": "4假設檢定與統計推論",
      "pageIndex": 12,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        703.47,
        231.76,
        718.48
      ],
      "id": "block-61",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 4,
      "text": "在機器學習與資料分析中，我們常遇到需要根據有限樣本，推論整體資料或模型是否具備某種統計性質。例如，某個特徵是否與目標變數顯著相關、兩種模",
      "pageIndex": 12,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        730.78,
        517.93,
        767.74
      ],
      "id": "block-62",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 4,
      "text": "型的表現差異是否具有統計意義等。這些問題皆屬於統計推論（Statistical Inference）的範疇，而假設檢定（Hypothesis Testing）則是其中最常用的工具之一。",
      "pageIndex": 13,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        100.82,
        521.88,
        139.07
      ],
      "id": "block-63",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "depth": 4,
      "title": "（1）統計推論",
      "anchor": "1統計推論",
      "pageIndex": 13,
      "bbox": [
        70.24,
        175.82,
        155.2,
        189.11
      ],
      "id": "block-64",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "統計推論的核心任務，是利用樣本資料對母體參數或模型行為進行估計與判斷，並量化不確定性。透過統計方法，我們可以推斷模型訓練的結果是否穩定、資料特徵之間是否存在顯著差異、以及模型選擇是否具有合理依據。",
      "pageIndex": 13,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        201.38,
        518.0,
        262.7
      ],
      "id": "block-65",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "統計推論可概略分為兩大核心分支：參數估計（Parameter Estimation）與假設檢定（Hypothesis Testing），兩者雖然目的不同，但均依賴機率模型作為推論依據，",
      "pageIndex": 13,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        273.89,
        521.23,
        311.66
      ],
      "id": "block-66",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "depth": 5,
      "rows": [
        [
          "並對樣本中的不確定性進行量化處理。\n參數估計",
          "統計假設檢定\n項目",
          ""
        ],
        [
          "目的",
          "推測母體參數的「值」或「區間」",
          "驗證某個關於母體參數的「主張」是\n否成立"
        ],
        [
          "重點問題",
          "這個母體參數大約是多少？（例如：\n平均收入是多少？）",
          "我們是否有足夠證據拒絕一個假\n設？（例如：新藥是否有效？）"
        ],
        [
          "輸出結果",
          "提供點估計值（如平均數）與信賴區\n間（如 95% CI）",
          "提供 p 值、檢定統計量，並根據顯著\n水準決定是否拒絕虛無假設"
        ],
        [
          "依據",
          "基於樣本資料，計算出母體參數的\n估計值",
          "基於假設前提與樣本結果，進行推\n論判斷"
        ],
        [
          "例子",
          "根據樣本估計出平均體重為 68 公\n斤，95%信賴區間為[66, 70]",
          "假設新運動課程能降低體重，檢定\n結果 p = 0.03，小於設定的 α值 0.05。\n因此拒絕虛無零假設，認為有效"
        ]
      ],
      "pageIndex": 13,
      "bbox": [
        72.94,
        327.49,
        523.44,
        572.49
      ],
      "id": "block-67",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "table",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "depth": 4,
      "title": "（2）假設檢定",
      "anchor": "2假設檢定",
      "pageIndex": 13,
      "bbox": [
        70.24,
        590.59,
        155.2,
        603.88
      ],
      "id": "block-68",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "假設檢定是一種以機率模型為基礎的推論方法，用於檢視樣本資料是否提供足夠證據來拒絕某一原先的假設。整體流程包含：",
      "pageIndex": 13,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        616.18,
        518.27,
        652.87
      ],
      "id": "block-69",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "A.",
      "text": "設定虛無假設（或稱零假設）與對立假設",
      "pageIndex": 13,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        664.18,
        325.29,
        677.47
      ],
      "id": "block-70",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "B.",
      "text": "選擇適當的檢定方法與檢定統計量",
      "pageIndex": 13,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        688.66,
        287.47,
        701.95
      ],
      "id": "block-71",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "C.",
      "text": "決定顯著水準",
      "pageIndex": 13,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        713.14,
        174.04,
        726.43
      ],
      "id": "block-72",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "D.",
      "text": "計算檢定統計量與p 值",
      "pageIndex": 13,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        737.62,
        224.47,
        750.91
      ],
      "id": "block-73",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "E.",
      "text": "比較顯著水準（α）並進行決策",
      "pageIndex": 13,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        762.1,
        268.87,
        775.38
      ],
      "id": "block-74",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "depth": 4,
      "title": "（3）顯著水準（α）與p 值",
      "anchor": "3顯著水準與p值",
      "pageIndex": 14,
      "bbox": [
        70.24,
        100.82,
        226.03,
        114.11
      ],
      "id": "block-75",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "在進行假設檢定之前，研究者需預先設定一個可接受的錯誤機率上限，稱為顯著水準（α）。顯著水準代表在虛無假設為真的前提下，仍可能因樣本隨機波動而錯誤地拒絕該假設的機率，也就是型一錯誤（Type I Error）發生的機率。",
      "pageIndex": 14,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        126.86,
        518.4,
        189.11
      ],
      "id": "block-76",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 5,
      "text": "而p 值則是在觀察到樣本資料後所計算出的機率，用來衡量資料與虛無假設的相符程度。",
      "pageIndex": 14,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        200.78,
        518.23,
        239.15
      ],
      "id": "block-77",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "depth": 3,
      "title": "5. 統計量與機器學習中的應用",
      "anchor": "5統計量與機器學習中的應用",
      "pageIndex": 14,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        274.66,
        274.0,
        289.67
      ],
      "id": "block-78",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 4,
      "text": "除了選擇適當的分佈型態，統計量（Statistical Measures）是用以描述資料分佈特性的重要指標，能夠協助分析者快速掌握變數的整體趨勢、變異程度與潛在異常。這些統計量廣泛應用於機器學習各階段，從前期的資料探索與特徵工程，到後期的模型訓練與效能評估，皆是不可或缺的輔助工具。",
      "pageIndex": 14,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        300.89,
        518.37,
        389.18
      ],
      "id": "block-79",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 4,
      "text": "在資料前處理與探索階段，統計量有助於確認變數的分佈型態與異常狀況，進而決定後續的標準化、轉換或篩選策略。常見應用如下：",
      "pageIndex": 14,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        401.93,
        517.93,
        439.1
      ],
      "id": "block-80",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "期望值（Expected Value）：反映變數的平均趨勢，為許多模型的預測基準與參數估計核心，例如線性迴歸中的截距項。",
      "pageIndex": 14,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        450.75,
        518.08,
        489.16
      ],
      "id": "block-81",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "變異數（Variance）與標準差（Standard Deviation）：衡量資料的離散程度，能判斷特徵是否需進行標準化處理，避免尺度不一致對模型訓練造成偏誤。",
      "pageIndex": 14,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        500.67,
        518.23,
        539.2
      ],
      "id": "block-82",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "偏態（Skewness）：判斷分佈是否對稱，若偏態過大，常需對變數進行對數轉換或Box-Cox 轉換，以改善模型收斂性與預測穩定性。",
      "pageIndex": 14,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        550.71,
        518.06,
        589.12
      ],
      "id": "block-83",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "list_item",
      "depth": 5,
      "marker": "•",
      "text": "峰度（Kurtosis）：觀察資料是否具有尖峰或厚尾，亦可作為偵測異常值密度與風險擴散的一項參考指標。",
      "pageIndex": 14,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        600.75,
        518.0,
        639.19
      ],
      "id": "block-84",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "source": "page_extract"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "depth": 4,
      "text": "這些統計量常透過視覺化方式（如直方圖、箱型圖、QQ-plot）輔助解釋，幫助分析者理解資料行為模式，並確認是否需採取分群處理、變數轉換或資料清理等動作。",
      "pageIndex": 14,
      "bbox": [
        76.6,
        659.02,
        518.31,
        722.35
      ],
      "id": "block-85",
      "nodeId": "mid-s3c1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "source": "page_extract"
    }
  ],
